@*
    ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    CymBuild EditPage
    ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    PURPOSE:
    Metadata-driven dynamic edit page for all CymBuild entities.
    Supports dynamic rendering, inline validation, SignalR live updates, AI error tracking,
    and metadata-bound field logic via `FormBody`, `DataObject`, and `EntityProperties`.

    🔁 REPLACES:
    Static, entity-specific forms
    ➜
    A universal editing surface for any entity type, driven by backend metadata.

    📒 FEATURES:
    - Dynamic entity editing powered by `dataObject.DataProperties`
    - Two-way model binding via `_editContext`
    - Save, Save & Exit, and dynamic task menu (`ButtonMenu`)
    - SignalR live sync support (for multi-user edit/locks/etc.)
    - AI-driven error capture (`AiErrorReporter`)
    - Modal photo and camera launcher for job-linked galleries
    - Detail and Info modal launchers via metadata URIs
    - Dynamic toolbar and back-to-top UX
    - Optional file channel for background uploads

    🧠 LOGIC:
    - NavigationLock for unsaved changes detection
    - Form submission buttons adjust based on validation state
    - Auto-disables Save if validation fails or no changes made
    - Launches detail/info modals using `DynamicComponent` + `EntityProperty.DetailPageUri`
    - AI overlay shows error or sync messages dynamically

    🛠️ DEPENDENCIES:
    - Core.CoreClient, SageIntegrationClient, StateService, ModalService
    - Blazor’s NavigationManager, IJSRuntime, IConfiguration
    - Services: `UserService`, `UserInteractionTrackerService`, `AiErrorReporter`
    - Components: `FormBody`, `ButtonMenu`, `MessageDisplay`, `CustomErrorBoundary`
    - Telerik UI and Bootstrap

    🔐 SAFETY:
    - Custom error boundary wrapping child content
    - Graceful fallbacks via `ErrorContent` if exception is raised

    🧪 QA & UI ENHANCEMENTS:
    - Overlay messaging with fade for background actions
    - Live file/image capture and gallery trigger for specific entity types
    - Dynamic field rendering logs tracked via `UserInteractionTrackerService`
    - Mobile-aware logic for modal/dialog launching and visibility

    ⚠️ KNOWN USAGE:
    - Used across all main CRUD operations in CymBuild
    - Works alongside dynamic grids, dashboard entries, and workflows

    📎 RELATED FILES:
    - `EditPage.razor.cs` (code-behind)
    - `FormHelper.cs` (gRPC interactions)
    - `DynamicInputRenderer.razor` (nested input controls per field)
    - `SignatureControl.razor`, `Trackable*` components for input instrumentation

*@

@page "/edit"
@using Concursus.API.Client.Models
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.SignalR.Client
@using Google.Protobuf.WellKnownTypes
@using System.Threading.Channels
@using Concursus.PWA.Services
@using Concursus.Components.Shared.Services

@inject Core.CoreClient coreClient
@inject NavigationManager NavManager
@inject IJSRuntime JsRuntime
@inject UserService userService
@inject Sage200Microservice.API.Protos.Invoice.InvoiceService.InvoiceServiceClient sageIntegrationService
@inject StateService stateService
@inject ModalService modalService
@inject RefreshService refreshService
@inject Channel<FileModel> _fileChannel
@inject IConfiguration Configuration
@inject AiErrorReporter AiErrorReporter
@inject UserInteractionTrackerService InteractionTracker
@inherits CustomErrorBoundary

<MessageDisplay @ref="_messageDisplay" ErrorMessage="@ErrorMessage" PageMethod="@PageMethod" MessageType="MessageType" />
<CustomErrorBoundary @ref="_customErrorBoundary">
    <ChildContent>
        <div class="@DialogCss" tabindex="-1" z-index="100">
            <!-- OE - Fix for CBLD-140-->
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h5 class="modal-title">Exit Page</h5>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close" @onclick=this.Cancel></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <p>Changes have been made, Are you sure you want to exit without saving?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" @onclick=this.Navigate>Yes</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" @onclick=this.Cancel>Cancel</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <NavigationLock OnBeforeInternalNavigation=this.OnNavigation />

        <EditForm EditContext="@_editContext">
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between">

                <div class="p-2">
                    <h4>
                        <i class="@EntityTypeIcon"></i> @EntityTypeLabel :- <small class="text-muted">@ObjectLabel</small>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div class="p-2 form-buttons d-flex align-items-center">

                    @* Centralised flags so we don't miss any button *@
                    @{
                        var hideActions = HideDefaultActions;
                        var disableActions = DisableDefaultActions;
                    }

                    @if (!hideActions)
                    {
                        @if (dataObject.DataProperties.Count > 0)
                        {
                            @if (!IsInformationPage && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(@ReturnUrl))
                            {
                                @FormButtons

                                @if (!IsBulkUpdate)
                                {
                                    @* --------------------------
                                       Gallery / Camera (existing)
                                       -------------------------- *@
                                    @if (EntityTypeGuid == "571a9397-7e28-4bef-8ddc-fd4c56787bde")
                                    {
                                        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(dataObject?.SharePointUrl))
                                        {
                                            @if (NumberOfPhotos > 0)
                                            {
                                                <span class="badge bg-success me-2">
                                                    @NumberOfPhotos Photos
                                                </span>
                                            }

                                            <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center">
                                                <button type="button"
                                                        class="btn btn-secondary me-2 custom-button"
                                                        title="Open Gallery"
                                                        @onclick="OpenGallery"
                                                        disabled="@(disableActions || SaveButtonDisabled || dataObject.HasValidationMessages)">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-images"></i>
                                                    <span class="sr-only"></span>
                                                </button>
                                            </div>

                                            <button type="button"
                                                    class="btn btn-secondary me-2 custom-button"
                                                    title="Open Camera"
                                                    @onclick="OpenCamera"
                                                    disabled="@(disableActions || SaveButtonDisabled || dataObject.HasValidationMessages)">
                                                <i class="bi bi-camera"></i>
                                                <span class="sr-only"></span>
                                            </button>
                                        }
                                    }

                                    @* --------------------------
                                       Tasks menu (ButtonMenu)
                                       NOTE: ButtonMenu has no Disabled parameter, so we gate it here.
                                       -------------------------- *@
                                    @if (!disableActions)
                                    {
                                        <div class="btn btn-primary form-action-menu" id="taskMenubtn">
                                            <ButtonMenu @ref="_buttonMenuRef"
                                                        dataObject="@dataObject"
                                                        GridUpdated="@GridUpdated"
                                                        ParentDataObjectReference="MyDataObjectReference"
                                                        ReturnUrl="@ReturnUrl"
                                                        EntityProperties="@entityProperties"
                                                        ParentGuid="@MyDataObjectReference.DataObjectGuid.ToString()"
                                                        EntityTypeGuid="@EntityTypeGuid"
                                                        OnError="@OnError"
                                                        OnClose="@CloseWindow"
                                                        RecieveItemDoubleClick="@ReceiveItemDoubleClick"
                                                        ReSyncDataObject="@ReSyncDataObject"
                                                        SaveDataObject="@SaveDataObject"
                                                        DeleteOperationPerformed="@DeleteOperationPerformed"
                                                        DeleteOperationPerformedChanged="@((value) => DeleteOperationPerformed = value)" 
                                                        @bind-HasChanges="@HasChanges"/>
                                        </div>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        @* Disabled placeholder so the header layout stays consistent *@
                                        <button type="button"
                                                class="btn btn-primary me-2"
                                                title="Tasks are disabled in this context"
                                                disabled="disabled">
                                            Tasks
                                        </button>
                                    }

                                    @* --------------------------
                                       Save buttons (existing logic preserved)
                                       + we add disableActions into each case
                                       -------------------------- *@
                                    @if (@SaveButtonDisabled || DeleteOperationPerformed || disableActions)
                                    {
                                        <button class="btn btn-warning" type="button"
                                                @onclick="@(() => FormSubmitted(_editContext, true, false))"
                                                disabled="true">
                                            <i class="bi bi-save-fill"></i> Save
                                        </button>
                                        <button class="btn btn-warning" type="button"
                                                @onclick="@(() => FormSubmitted(_editContext, true, true))"
                                                disabled="true">
                                            <i class="bi bi-save-fill"></i> Save and Exit
                                        </button>
                                    }
                                    else if (HasValidationMessages)
                                    {
                                        <button class="btn btn-warning mb-1 disabled" type="button"
                                                @onclick="@(() => FormSubmitted(_editContext, true, false))" value="Save">
                                            <i class="bi bi-save-fill"></i> Save
                                        </button>
                                        <button class="btn btn-warning mb-1 disabled" type="button"
                                                @onclick="@(() => FormSubmitted(_editContext, true, true))" value="SaveExit">
                                            <i class="bi bi-save-fill"></i> Save and Exit
                                        </button>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <button class="btn btn-success" id="Savebtn" type="button"
                                                @onclick="@(() => FormSubmitted(_editContext, true, false))"
                                                disabled="@(disableActions)">
                                            <i class="bi bi-save-fill"></i> Save
                                        </button>
                                        <button class="btn btn-success" id="SaveAndExitbtn" type="button"
                                                @onclick="@(() => FormSubmitted(_editContext, true, true))"
                                                disabled="@(disableActions)">
                                            <i class="bi bi-save-fill"></i> Save and Exit
                                        </button>
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }

                    @* Keep overlay exactly as-is *@
                    @if (isPreparingStorageUrl)
                    {
                        <div class="loading-overlay">
                            <div class="spinner-border text-primary" role="status">
                                <span class="sr-only">Loading...</span>
                            </div>
                            <p>Preparing storage location...</p>
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
            @{
                // Job EntityTypeGuid: 63542427-46ab-4078-abd1-1d583c24315c
                var showFinancialOverview =
                string.Equals(EntityTypeGuid, "63542427-46ab-4078-abd1-1d583c24315c", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase);
            }

            <DataPillRow DataPills="@dataObject.DataPills.ToList()"
                         ShowFinancialOverview="@showFinancialOverview"
                         InvoiceProcessingModeText="@InvoiceProcessingModeText"
                         InvoiceProcessingModeCss="@InvoiceProcessingModeCss"
                         InvoiceProcessingModeTooltip="@InvoiceProcessingModeTooltip" />
            <div style="@(IsLoading ? "position: relative;" : "")">
                @if (IsLoading)
                {
                    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; left: 0; z-index: 1000; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"></div>
                }
                @FormBody
                @if (!@Windowed)
                {
                    <div class="back-to-top-button">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" @onclick="ScrollToTop">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-circle"></i> Back To Top
                        </button>
                    </div>
                }
                @if (_showOverlay)
                {
                    <div class="overlay">
                        <div class="overlay-content">
                            @foreach (var message in _messages)
                            {
                                <p>@message</p>
                            }
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </EditForm>
    </ChildContent>
    <ErrorContent Context="ex">
        <ErrorDisplay ErrorMessage="@ex.Message" />
    </ErrorContent>
</CustomErrorBoundary>

<style>
    .page li {
        font-size: 1.154rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .report-button-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .loader-indicator {
        margin-left: 5px;
    }

    .form-buttons .btn {
        margin-left: 0.25rem;
    }

    .overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 1050;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        pointer-events: none; /* Makes the overlay non-clickable */
    }

    .overlay-content {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-align: center;
    }

        .overlay-content p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

    .form-action-menu {
    }

        .form-action-menu .k-menu.k-menu-horizontal:not(.k-context-menu) {
            padding: 0;
        }

        .form-action-menu .k-in {
            padding-block: 0;
            padding-inline: 0;
        }

        .form-action-menu .k-menu:not(.k-context-menu) {
            background-color: transparent;
        }

            .form-action-menu .k-menu:not(.k-context-menu) > .k-item {
                color: #ffffff;
            }

        .form-action-menu .k-menu-link-text {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .form-action-menu .k-menu-vertical > .k-separator {
            border-color: Red;
        }

    .loading-indicator {
        border: 5px solid #f3f3f3; /* Light grey background */
        border-top: 5px solid #3498db; /* Blue spinner */
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
    }

    .back-to-top-button {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        z-index: 1000; /* Ensure it is on top of other elements */
        opacity: 0.5; /* Initial opacity lets set it to 50% */
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease; /* Smooth hover effect rather than instant change */
    }

        .back-to-top-button:hover {
            opacity: 1; /* Full opacity on hover */
        }

    .show-dialog {
        display: block;
    }

    .button-menu-container {
        gap: 10px; /* Adds spacing between flex items */
    }

    .custom-button {
        background-color: #007bff; /* Custom background color */
        border-color: #007bff;
    }

        .custom-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3; /* Darker background color on hover */
            border-color: #0056b3;
        }

    .loading-overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        z-index: 9999;
    }

        /*     .spinner-border {
                                                width: 3rem;
                                                height: 3rem;
                                                margin-right: 1rem;
                                            } */

        .loading-overlay p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

</style>